#### Options:

* __expandable__ | `boolean`: controls whether calculator is expandable. Default: `true`.
* __show__ | `boolean`: controls whether calculator is shown. Default: `true`.
* __style__ | `object`: CSS inline styles. Default: `{}`.
* __onHide__ | `function`: callback invoked when the close button is clicked. Default: `none`.
